25:54.587 --> 25:57.317
Did you ever get her name?

25:57.423 --> 25:59.323
Yeah, it was Athena.

25:59.425 --> 26:01.791
I was gonna marry her.

26:03.696 --> 26:05.823
You were gonna marry her?

26:07.199 --> 26:09.667
Yeah. I bought her
a ring and everything.

26:13.773 --> 26:17.209
