that you got your girl.

26:22.148 --> 26:26.778
I didn't steal your ring,
Henry, okay? I promise.

26:33.459 --> 26:35.359
Yeah, I lost it.

26:37.563 --> 26:40.430
Anyway, she's gone.

26:40.533 --> 26:43.468
- She's gone?
- Yeah.

26:43.569 --> 26:45.969
- Or she's somewhere else?
- What do you mean?

26:46.072 --> 26:48.472
There is no somewhere else.

26:58.684 --> 27:01.175
[Deep Growling]

27:11.797 --> 27:13.697
<i>[Man]</i>
<i>He's not going to make it.</i>

27:17.103 --> 27:20.300
[Growling Continues]

27:36.589 --> 27:39.353
- It's beautiful.
- No.

27:39.458 --> 27:42.723
It's like the crap
tourists buy on Fifth Avenue.

27:47.566 --> 27:51.400
- You talk with your student today?
- Mm-hmm.

27:53.305 --> 27:55.466
Still wants to do it?

27:55.574 --> 27:57.940
I don't feel right talking about it.

27:59.311 --> 28:01.677
Talking about it with me, you mean.

28:10.122 --> 28:12.522
You stopped taking your pills.

28:15.027 --> 28:17.757
I've been counting.
You haven't taken one in weeks.

28:17.863 --> 28:19.854
<i>I don't need 'em anymore.</i>

28:19.965 --> 28:22.900
Well, that's a decision
we should've made together.

28:23.002 --> 28:27.701
