I can't paint on meds.

28:30.843 --> 28:32.936
I can't.

28:36.949 --> 28:39.941
- [Sighs]
- <i>Well, it makes me nervous.</i>

28:40.052 --> 28:42.919
I'm not happy
you did this in secret.

28:43.022 --> 28:47.857
[Scoffs] Well, I'm not happy
you're counting my pills in secret.

28:47.960 --> 28:51.452
We have to trust each other.

28:57.069 --> 29:00.129
Hey, look at me.

29:05.010 --> 29:07.672
I can't make them disappear.

29:09.915 --> 29:11.906
I wish I could.

29:17.089 --> 29:19.455
I made you a promise.

29:20.960 --> 29:24.862
[Sighs]
I gotta go.

29:27.733 --> 29:29.633
I'll see you at home.

29:32.605 --> 29:37.702
<i>Henry?</i>
<i>Forgetting something?</i>

29:40.479 --> 29:44.176
- What's the matter?
- You just called me Henry.

29:44.283 --> 29:48.845
- <i>Baby, I think I know your name by now.</i>
- Yeah, but you called me Henry.

29:48.954 --> 29:52.651
Sam, I know who you are.
I promise.

29:54.160 --> 29:56.060
Sorry.

29:59.465 --> 30:01.365
Okay.

30:14.847 --> 30:16.747
