<i>Do you get nervous?</i>

30:16.982 --> 30:18.745
<i>[Woman]</i>
<i>Do you get nervous?</i>

30:18.851 --> 30:21.411
<i>It's a great part,</i>
<i>but she should resist more.</i>

30:21.520 --> 30:25.012
